fields.description:
In a view, if the LeftNavButtons tag does not have a body, it does not generate the declaration and instantiation of the variable {{leftNavButtons}}.  The same happens for {{rightNavButtons}} as well.

view xml

{code:xml}
<Alloy>
  <Window>
     <LeftNavButtons />
  </Window>
</Alloy>
{code}

error:


{noformat}
[ERROR] ReferenceError: Can't find variable: leftNavButtons
{noformat}
